  "texts": [
    "Pretext tasks allow the model to learn key characteristics from input data.",
    "Data augmentation to generate multiple perspectives of the same image and training the ViT model to predict which views match is a common pretext challenge.",
    "Contrastive learning teaches the ViT model to distinguish between similar and distinct images.",
    "Two arbitrary images are supplied to the ViT model.",
    "The model is then trained to predict whether or not two images are identical.In both cases, the ViT model discovers features that are independent of viewpoint, illumination, and other factors that affect the appearance of input data."
